<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head') %>
  <style>
    .twofa-container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
    }
    
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      background: #d4edda;
      color: #155724;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
  
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="twofa-container">
        <div class="card">
          <h1>🔐 双重认证</h1>
          
          <%- include('../partials/messages') %>
          
          <div class="text-center my-4">
            <div class="status-badge">
              ✓ 已启用
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="alert alert-info">
            <strong>双重认证已启用</strong>
            <p class="mb-0">您的账户已受到额外保护。每次登录时，除了密码，还需要输入身份验证器中的验证码。</p>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="mt-4">禁用双重认证</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">如果您想禁用双重认证，需要输入当前密码进行确认。</p>
          
          <form action="/2fa/disable" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">当前密码</label>
              <input 
                type="password" 
                name="password" 
                class="form-control" 
                required
              >
            </div>
            
            <div class="d-grid gap-2">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">禁用双重认证</button>
              <a href="/profile" class="btn btn-secondary">返回</a>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
